    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Environments during a fixed period in the past, usually predating historical records and often of the remote past, as reconstructed by such disciplines as paleobotany and environmental archaeology.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000088/GCI</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000062053/Encyclopedia of Archaeology [online] (2008)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000062045/Cloutman and Smith, Palaeoenvironments, Proceeding of the Prehistoric Society (1988)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Milieus gedurende een bepaalde periode in het verleden, meestal ouder dan er historische documenten zijn en vaak in het verre verleden, zoals gereconstrueerd in vakgebieden als paleobotanie en archeologische ecologie.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000109894/UvA Talen</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Umweltbedingungen während eines bestimmten Zeitraums in der Vergangenheit, der in der Regel vor historischen Aufzeichnungen liegt und oft weit zurückliegt, wie sie von Disziplinen wie der Paläobotanik und der Umweltarchäologie rekonstruiert werden.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
